headline: HSBC downgrades Autodesk on moderating earnings growth, valuation concerns
summary: Investing.com -- HSBC downgraded Autodesk Inc (NASDAQ:ADSK) to “hold” from “buy” as it expects moderating earnings growth and valuation concerns relative to peer Dassault Systèmes. Brokerage also lowered its target price on the stock by $9 to $290.
